title.narrative: Jilin Agricultural Product Safety and Quality

description.narrative: The objectives of the Project are to assist Jilin Province in improving its agricultural product quality and reducing agricultural product safety risks through: (i) introducing good agricultural practices, (ii) improving the implementation of agricultural product safety related regulations, and (iii) strengthening the agricultural product safety monitoring system.

Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section I, 2. | Description :Project entity shall prepare annual work and budget plan fro theBank's review | Due Date :31-Dec-2011
Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section I, 3. | Description :Project entity shall implement the project consistent with the ProjectImplementation Manual | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section I, 6. | Description :Sub-grant recipients shall enter into an Implementation Agreement withthe PMO | Due Date :30-Nov-2011

Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section I. 8. | Description :Jilin PPMO retain qualified technical and financial specialists toensure that the sub-loan beneficiaries and the sub-projects to be financed by the sub-loans meet the eligibility criteria |Frequency :Quarterly
Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section II. A. 2 | Description :Jilin PPMO submits the mid-term review report to the Bank | DueDate :31-Mar-2013
Finance Agreement :PA Schedule, Section II. A.1 | Description :Project progress report shall be submitted to the Bank no later thanMarch 31, and September 30 of each year | Frequency :Quarterly
